    <item>
      <title>IAG 提供修复方案以赢得欧盟批准 4 亿欧元收购欧罗巴航空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/iag-offers-fixes-to-win-eu-nod-for-400-million-air-europa-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国航空母公司 IAG SA 向欧盟竞争监管机构提出了新的让步，以缓解人们对其斥资 4 亿欧元（4.3 亿美元）收购欧洲航空的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/iag-offers-fixes-to-win-eu-nod-for-400-million-air-europa-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 10:10:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储长期维持高利率立场打击预期降息的公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/fed-s-higher-for-longer-stance-hits-firms-that-expected-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年年初，美国企业和消费者认为利率最终会下降，并制定了购买设备或房屋的大计划。但现在，所有这些都被搁置，在可预见的未来，经济的大部分领域都将放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/fed-s-higher-for-longer-stance-hits-firms-that-expected-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟出售 15 年期债券，指数纳入问题仍存疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/eu-sells-15-year-bond-as-questions-linger-over-index-inclusion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧盟债务是否会被纳入主要主权指数存在不确定性且极右翼政党激增导致投资者对法国经济信心受损的背景下，欧盟正在发行新债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/eu-sells-15-year-bond-as-questions-linger-over-index-inclusion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 09:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本确认下一财年基本收支盈余目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/japan-affirms-primary-balance-surplus-goal-for-next-fiscal-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本政府在周二发布的经济和财政政策计划草案中重申了在下一财年实现基本收支盈余的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/japan-affirms-primary-balance-surplus-goal-for-next-fiscal-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 09:48:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙辞职传闻导致法国债券价格创 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/french-yield-premium-over-germany-jumps-to-highest-since-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙决定提前举行大选后，有关他未来的谣言四起，法国债券价格暴跌，导致收益率出现自疫情爆发以来的两日最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/french-yield-premium-over-germany-jumps-to-highest-since-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 09:14:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国债券订单量达 1090 亿英镑，创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/uk-smashes-bond-sale-demand-record-with-104-billion-orderbook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国周二的政府债券发售订单量超过 1090 亿英镑（1390 亿美元），打破了债券需求纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/uk-smashes-bond-sale-demand-record-with-104-billion-orderbook</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 09:10:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克通胀放缓加剧央行利率困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/czech-inflation-drops-as-policymakers-debate-slower-easing-pace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克5月份通胀放缓幅度超过预期，这加深了该国央行在衡量国内价格趋势与主要经济体利率前景不明朗之际的政策困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/czech-inflation-drops-as-policymakers-debate-slower-easing-pace</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 07:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
